            <title><![CDATA[冠病感染激增加剧药物短缺 中国药企春节前铆足劲解缺药之急]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2023-01/ZB_0111_CJ_doc7ofd1m8ccyxtpv4doa_10171107_singsc.jpg?itok=VIg4-pwD" title="悦康药业的退烧药生产线24小时连轴转，每日产量增至15万盒，但仍供不应求。（杨丹旭摄）" alt="悦康药业的退烧药生产线24小时连轴转，每日产量增至15万盒，但仍供不应求。（杨丹旭摄）" src="https://www.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2023-01/ZB_0111_CJ_doc7ofd1m8ccyxtpv4doa_10171107_singsc.jpg?itok=VIg4-pwD" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
