            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2023-01/50834047_bloomberg_china_reopens.jpg?VersionId=fnSEW79eAtViOUkrQZqM83cxFDCJNXsA&amp;itok=xs5jJIuK" title="中国在冠病疫情暴发三年后重开国门，许多人久别重逢。一名小孩穿着熊猫服装，在北京首都国际机场接机。（彭博社）" alt="中国在冠病疫情暴发三年后重开国门，许多人久别重逢。一名小孩穿着熊猫服装，在北京首都国际机场接机。（彭博社）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2023-01/50834047_bloomberg_china_reopens.jpg?VersionId=fnSEW79eAtViOUkrQZqM83cxFDCJNXsA&amp;itok=xs5jJIuK" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
